author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Actor Chris Hemsworth joins Instagram
text:
Richard Shotwell/Richard Shotwell/Invision/AP Actor Chris Hemsworth finally creates an Instagram account. Hunky Australian actor Chris Hemsworth joined Instagram on Monday and posted his first picture posing with a snake.
In the photo, the “ Thor” star also might have referred to actor Chris Pratt with a subtle dig.

“Hangin’ with the locals in my backyard...the real Jurassic Park,” Hemsworth said in the caption of the photo posted Monday.
